    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project? This car is a fantastic opportunity for a handy owner or someone looking for a budget-friendly fixer-upper! While it currently needs some mechanical repairs and cosmetic attention, it's a vehicle with great potential for the right person. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own!",
