    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s super reliable and a total blast to drive? You\u2019ve found it! This car has been so good to me and it's still in really solid, well-loved shape. It runs like a dream and is just waiting for someone new to take it on its next big adventure. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or those fun weekend road trips. Come check it out and see for yourself\u2014you're going to love how it feels on the road!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
