      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example is mechanically sorted, with the critical dual-VANOS system recently overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced with integrated plates to address factory stress-point vulnerabilities. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed control arm bushings and a Bilstein B16 adjustable coilover suite, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited road use, the drivetrain is robust, benefiting from a recent valve adjustment and cooling system refresh. A tactically maintained driver's car that delivers a pure, analog performance experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
